** ERR (40A) ......2.........3.........4
ENTER INVOICE DATE!                      01
SHIFT CODE SHOULD BE 1, 2 OR 3!          02
NO TARGET DATA!                          03
SELECT 1,2,3,4 OR 5 FOR PRINTER!         04
DATE IS NOT CORRECT!                     05
PRESS F5 OR F6...                        06
